        "t_69c38a12": "Order Confirmed - L'Olio di Valeria",
        "t_d9a9f991": "Checkout - L'Olio di Valeria | Secure Payment",
        "t_1e899148": "<nav class=\"breadcrumb-nav\"> <a href=\"index.html\">Home</a> <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right\"></i> <span class=\"current\" data-i18n=\"header.chi_siamo\">Our Story</span> </nav>",
        "t_92fd232a": "Sicilian tradition since 1987",
        "t_6217aa53": "Our Story",
        "t_4d92a7cd": "Three generations of passion for extra virgin olive oil",
        "t_e5f0b713": "Our history originates from the lands of San Biagio Platani, in the province of Agrigento: a family story that has been bringing the authentic flavor of Sicily to tables around the world for over 35 years.",
        "t_186a2179": "The Founder",
        "t_b87d7135": "Valeria and Her Roots",
        "t_a9267473": "It all begins in the hills of the <span class=\"highlight\">Monti Sicani</span>, on a land lovingly cultivated by our ancestors. From these deep roots was born an indissoluble bond with nature and the territory, which was transformed into meticulous care for the olive trees. Grandfather Agostino dedicated his life to these trees, producing an <span class=\"highlight\">extra virgin olive oil</span> which, for generations, was the exclusive treasure of our family, synonymous with <span class=\"highlight\">authenticity</span> and <span class=\"highlight\">unrivaled quality</span>.",
        "t_743abb4e": "After Agostino's passing, his son Salvatore felt the desire to honor his father's work and legacy. This <span class=\"highlight\">passion</span>, combined with the desire to share such a special product with the world, led him to transform tradition into a business: thus <span class=\"highlight\">Olio di Valeria</span> was born. The name is a tribute to his wife Valeria, pillar of the family, who with her innate elegance was able to elevate the company, carefully taking care of the quality of the <span class=\"highlight\">100% organic</span> oil and the refined aesthetics of the <span class=\"highlight\">packaging</span>.",
        "t_15c0eb0f": "Today the company is a harmonious balance between past and future. Salvatore and Valeria are supported by their son Agostino, who carries on his grandfather's name and mission. With the same respect for the land, Agostino takes care of every single tree and olive, guaranteeing the rigorous <span class=\"highlight\">organic standard</span> and the excellence of our <span class=\"highlight\">L'Olio di Valeria</span>. This oil is the essence of our family, a symbol of <span class=\"highlight\">Authenticity</span>, <span class=\"highlight\">Tradition</span> and <span class=\"highlight\" data-i18n=\"header.qualita\">Quality</span> that we proudly bring to your table.",
        "t_8dc6d39d": "Our Philosophy",
        "t_b064c691": "Values ​​and Tradition",
        "t_b395db7e": "Each bottle of L'Olio di Valeria contains the values ​​that guide our production: authenticity, sustainability and respect for Sicilian tradition.",
        "t_f976bf30": "Manual collection",
        "t_35b96728": "Each olive is harvested strictly by hand at the perfect moment of ripeness, guaranteeing the highest quality and preserving the integrity of the fruit.",
        "t_3ea739a3": "Cold pressing",
        "t_798bce19": "The pressing takes place within 24 hours of harvesting, using exclusively the cold extraction method to preserve all the organoleptic properties.",
        "t_37d73283": "Sustainability",
        "t_68c1fb11": "We cultivate our olive groves with sustainable methods, respecting the environment and preserving the biodiversity of the Sicilian lands for future generations.",
        "t_2a10c57d": "Certified Quality",
        "t_35caca3b": "Our oils have obtained recognition for quality and purity, testifying to the excellence of Sicilian artisanal production.",
        "t_00e7a8d4": "Family Passion",
        "t_b601732d": "Three generations of the family dedicate themselves to production with love and dedication, passing down secrets and traditions that make each of our oils unique.",
        "t_9a908c16": "Cultural Heritage",
        "t_12bb71b9": "We preserve and share the cultural heritage of Sicilian oil, bringing the authentic flavor and soul of our land into the world.",
        "t_f8572d43": "A Story of Growth",
        "t_aa5c6b47": "From the foundation to today, a journey made of passion, innovation and respect for tradition.",
        "t_aa713e4e": "The Foundation",
        "t_dd54f629": "The foundation of Our Family Estate in San Biagio Platani, inheriting the passion and secrets handed down from grandparents for the production of extra virgin olive oil.",
        "t_89a27c1c": "First Awards",
        "t_c63b2697": "L'Olio di Valeria obtains the first recognitions for its superior quality, starting to make itself known beyond regional borders.",
        "t_bf376823": "National expansion",
        "t_ad97bf78": "The company expands reaching restaurants and specialized ONLINE SHOPs throughout Italy, bringing Sicilian authenticity to national tables.",
        "t_9bee4abc": "Quality Certifications",
        "t_199dea40": "Obtaining the main quality and purity certifications, confirming the excellence of artisanal production.",
        "t_728e35d2": "Present and Future",
        "t_c580917e": "Today L'Olio di Valeria continues to grow, keeping intact the values ​​of tradition and quality that have made it a Sicilian excellence.",
        "t_63b7a225": "Our Mission",
        "t_5da80efb": "Sharing the Soul of Sicily",
        "t_657fd997": "Our mission is simple but profound: <span class=\"highlight\">to share with the world the authentic flavor and soul of true Sicily</span> through our superior quality extra virgin olive oil.",
        "t_500cbcdb": "Every bottle we produce is a bridge between our Agrigento lands and the tables of those seeking the <span class=\"highlight\">authenticity and genuineness</span> of Sicilian artisanal products.",
        "t_35bd259d": "We are proud to preserve and pass on the <span class=\"highlight\">cultural heritage</span> of Sicilian oil, helping to keep alive the traditions that make our land unique and its unmistakable flavours.",
        "t_06a6107a": "On Television",
        "t_ca847d44": "L'OLIO DI VALERIA arrives on TV",
        "t_663042f0": "<span style=\"color: #eab308; font-weight: 600;\">Mariagrazia Cucinetto</span> has selected our 100% CERTIFIED ORGANIC among many others, appreciating its delicate taste, the authentic aroma of olives and the unique ability to enhance each dish with flavor and harmony, making it truly unforgettable.",
        "t_c6c02273": "Taste the Tradition",
        "t_d6284486": "Discover the authentic flavor of Sicily with our superior quality extra virgin oils. Every drop tells a story of passion, tradition and love for the land.",
        "t_be96ce69": "<a class=\"btn-primary\" href=\"shop.html\"> <i class=\"fas fa-shopping-cart\"></i> <span>Discover Our Oils</span> </a> <a class=\"btn-secondary\" href=\"contatti.html\"> <i class=\"fas fa-envelope\"></i> <span>Contact us</span> </a>",
        "t_3287f745": "Our Story - L'Olio di Valeria | Sicilian history and tradition since 1987",
        "t_e4c94b77": "<a class=\"active\" href=\"contatti.html\">Contacts</a>",
        "t_07bd2608": "<nav class=\"breadcrumb-nav\"> <a href=\"index.html\">Home</a> <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right\"></i> <span class=\"current\">Contacts</span> </nav>",
        "t_8e6001d5": "Let's talk about Sicilian oil",
        "t_0dc460f5": "Let's get in touch",
        "t_ad34f3a8": "Let's get in touch to share our passion for Sicilian extra virgin olive oil. Whether you have questions about our products, want to learn more about our history, or are interested in collaborations, we'd love to hear from you.",
