        "t_78c21fad": "The Nearby Cities <div class=\"distance-row\"> <span class=\"city-name\">Agrigento</span> <span class=\"distance\">36.7 km</span> </div> <div class=\"distance-row\"> <span class=\"city-name\">Palermo</span> <span class=\"distance\">114.3 km</span> </div> <div class=\"distance-row\"> <span class=\"city-name\">Trapani</span> <span class=\"distance\">173.8 km</span> </div> <div class=\"distance-row\"> <span class=\"city-name\">Catania</span> <span class=\"distance\">193.2 km</span> </div> <div class=\"distance-row\"> <span class=\"city-name\">Messina</span> <span class=\"distance\">288.7 km</span> </div>",
        "t_4d961f84": "🛣️ Directions",
        "t_50861a31": "How to reach us",
        "t_1b5bcf76": "We are waiting for you in San Biagio Platani. Here are the driving directions from the main Sicilian cities.",
        "t_421e56b2": "<div class=\"direction-icon\">🚗</div> <span>From Palermo</span>",
        "t_2b5a8dae": "<strong>Palermo – Agrigento State Road</strong>. Take the junction for <strong>Casteltermini</strong>, continue towards <strong>San Biagio Platani</strong> for another 17 km.",
        "t_abec2720": "<div class=\"direction-icon\">🚗</div> <span>From Catania</span>",
        "t_fb66d404": "<strong>Caltanissetta – Agrigento</strong>. Take the exit towards <strong>Raffadali</strong> and continue towards <strong>Santa Elisabetta</strong>, follow the signs for <strong>San Biagio Platani</strong>.",
        "t_1c519c2b": "<div class=\"direction-icon\">🚗</div> <span>From Trapani</span>",
        "t_7b1ae462": "Along the <strong>SS115</strong> towards <strong>Agrigento-Siracusa</strong>, exit at <strong>Siculiana</strong> and continue crossing <strong>Raffadali</strong>. Follow signs for <strong>Santa Elisabetta</strong> and <strong>Sant'Angelo Muxaro</strong>, continue for <strong>San Biagio Platani</strong>.",
        "t_8e5b4103": "✈️ By Plane",
        "t_6a889d15": "Airports in Sicily",
        "t_c4f091a3": "To reach us by plane, Sicily has 4 international airports.",
        "t_91667673": "PMO",
        "t_63a1a455": "Falcone e Borsellino International Airport of Palermo-Punta Raisi",
        "t_a9fd8f82": "CTA",
        "t_2e3f53d6": "Vincenzo Bellini International Airport of Catania-Fontanarossa",
        "t_03859a04": "TPS",
        "t_c52eaeb1": "Trapani-Birgi Vincenzo Florio Airport",
        "t_e20bb369": "CIY",
        "t_09973689": "Pio la Torre Airport in Comiso",
        "t_74751b9b": "🗺️ Interactive Map",
        "t_6e42095c": "The Platani Valley",
        "t_ec7eef05": "San Biagio Platani is located in the heart of the Platani Valley, one of the most evocative areas of the Agrigento hinterland, surrounded by hills planted with centuries-old olive trees.",
        "t_df2b6d45": "🧭 Open in Google Maps",
        "t_3037115e": "San Biagio Platani Extra Virgin Olive Oil | L'Olio di Valeria - Agrigento Sicily",
        "t_019cb5b8": "<nav class=\"breadcrumb-nav\"> <a href=\"index.html\">Home</a> <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right\"></i> <span class=\"current\">FAQ</span> </nav>",
        "t_4be4d66a": "❓ Frequently Asked Questions",
        "t_1fe917b0": "FAQ",
        "t_87a5ac6c": "Our FAQ answers the most frequently asked questions about products, shipping and services",
        "t_5e6b2bdd": "Do you ship internationally? <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down faq-icon\"></i>",
        "t_a5c65810": "We currently ship throughout Italy and some European Union countries. For international shipments outside the EU, please contact us directly to check availability and shipping costs.",
        "t_235ac756": "When will I receive my order? <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down faq-icon\"></i>",
        "t_ee023670": "Orders are processed within 1-2 business days. Standard shipping takes 3-5 business days to Italy. For urgent shipments, we also offer an express service with delivery within 24-48 hours.",
        "t_8282ec45": "I got the damaged goods wrong, what do I do? <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down faq-icon\"></i>",
        "t_d2774f84": "In case of goods damaged in transit, please contact us immediately with photos of the damage. We will replace the product free of charge as quickly as possible.",
        "t_38feac74": "I forgot a product, how do I add it to the order? <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down faq-icon\"></i>",
        "t_58db0aea": "If your order has not yet been shipped, you can contact us to add products. If it has already been shipped, you will need to place a new, separate order.",
        "t_b0714a30": "Can I order products to be sent with the gift box? <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down faq-icon\"></i>",
        "t_783465ad": "Certainly! We offer elegant gift packaging for all our products. You can select this option during checkout and also add a personalized message.",
        "t_e4fecbd4": "Products and Conservation",
        "t_d89d616c": "Does olive oil have an expiration date? <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down faq-icon\"></i>",
        "t_2d02eb48": "Our extra virgin olive oil has a shelf life of 18 months from the date of production if stored correctly. The expiry date is always indicated on the product label.",
        "t_19acb9c4": "What is the best method for storing oil? <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down faq-icon\"></i>",
        "t_dd25bf12": "The oil must be stored in a cool, dry place and away from direct light. The ideal temperature is between 14-18°C. Avoid storing it near heat sources or in the refrigerator.",
        "t_32f65952": "General",
        "t_3614bb91": "Something wrong happened. How can I contact you? <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down faq-icon\"></i>",
        "t_773e7228": "You can contact us by email, telephone or through our social channels. All our contacts are available in the \"Contacts\" section of the site. We will respond as quickly as possible.",
        "t_0c92b692": "FAQ - Frequently Asked Questions | L'Olio di Valeria - Sicilian Oil",
