        "t_f83f0b6d": "100% CERTIFIED ORGANIC EXTRA VIRGIN",
        "t_567827f3": "<span>THE TRUE OLIVE OIL</span><br/> <span class=\"hero-subtitle\">ORGANIC & EXTRA VIRGIN</span>",
        "t_c48da1c0": "100% organic and vegan extra virgin olive oil from the hills of San Biagio Platani, Sicily. Authentic tradition, certified quality.",
        "t_8abed643": "<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"shop.html\">DISCOVER OUR PRODUCTS</a> <a class=\"btn btn-outline\" href=\"chisiamo.html\">OUR HISTORY</a>",
        "t_4bdae9b0": "L'OLIO DI VALERIA",
        "t_4ab06444": "L'Olio di Valeria is a 100% certified organic superior category extra virgin olive oil.",
        "t_9afd3316": "Sicily is one of the most important regions in Italy for the production of superior quality extra virgin olive oil.",
        "t_95809440": "Our lands of San Biagio Platani, in the province of Agrigento, boast an olive oil tradition of excellence. With our production we are honored to represent the best of <span class=\"highlight\">made in Italy</span>, offering a refined and appreciated extra virgin olive oil on the tables of consumers all over the world.",
        "t_abb31438": "<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"shop.html\"> VISIT OUR PRODUCTS </a>",
        "t_81e05cbf": "<i class=\"fas fa-crown\"></i> <span>Sicilian Family Business</span>",
        "t_18068e20": "The Oil of<br/> <span style=\"color: #eab308;\">Valeria</span>",
        "t_fc0bac72": "It is a purely <span class=\"highlight\">family-run farm founded in <span class=\"year\">1987</span> in <span class=\"FIND US\">San Biagio Platani (AG)</span>, specialized in the production and distribution of <span class=\"quality\">Certified Quality Sicilian Extra Virgin Olive Oil</span>.",
        "t_644e6347": "Catering",
        "t_d5aca3e3": "For professional chefs",
        "t_f1c4e4f9": "Specialties",
        "t_e512cfa9": "Grocery stores",
        "t_0828abc6": "Gourmet",
        "t_18f9a6c8": "Refined palates",
        "t_4b34dc1b": "<a class=\"btn btn-gradient\" href=\"chisiamo.html\"> <span>OUR STORY</span> <div style=\"margin-left: 8px;\">→</div> </a> <a class=\"btn btn-yellow-outline\" data-i18n=\"header.company\" href=\"aziendaagr.html\"> Our Family Estate </a> <!-- to be updated --> <a class=\"btn btn-yellow\" href=\"galleria.html\"> GALLERY </a>",
        "t_5c375842": "Years of Experience",
        "t_2e2074b2": "Generations",
        "t_a8a02e77": "Our Products",
        "t_c6762b6b": "Discover our selection of Sicilian extra virgin olive oils, each with unique characteristics and distinctive flavors of the Agrigento lands.",
        "t_9d442d54": "MARASCA",
        "t_3e64cbc1": "L'OLIO DI VALERIA",
        "t_5282d2cf": "Discover and Buy",
        "t_c5c2244c": "GRANDOLIO",
        "t_def7b93d": "From €11.99",
        "t_6e3ad117": "SHOULDER",
        "t_23ae1a46": "Discover the entire catalogue",
        "t_c91c7688": "Explore all our formats and limited editions dedicated to true lovers of Sicilian oil.",
        "t_e06af5b5": "<span>GO TO THE ONLINE SHOP</span> <i class=\"fas fa-arrow-right\"></i>",
        "t_e6833adf": "<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"shop.html\">SEE ALL PRODUCTS</a>",
        "t_899e56bd": "Why Choose L'Olio di Valeria",
        "t_57595837": "Superior Quality",
        "t_30055871": "Top quality Sicilian extra virgin olive oil, cold extracted to preserve all the nutrients and authentic flavor of our lands.",
        "t_dcc63131": "100% Organic",
        "t_932d4b7c": "Produced without chemical additives, using only Sicilian olives hand-selected with care and passion in the lands of San Biagio Platani.",
        "t_b86c6d66": "Since 1987, three generations of the family have passionately dedicated themselves to the production of superior quality extra virgin olive oil, passing down Sicilian traditions and family secrets.",
        "t_c7ac06bf": "The <span class=\"highlight\">Traditional Sicilian Harvest</span>",
        "t_0518a8ad": "Each olive is harvested at the perfect moment of ripeness in our lands of San Biagio Platani, guaranteeing the highest quality of our extra virgin oil. Sicilian tradition combines with passion to offer a unique product.",
        "t_8dfd9785": "Manual harvesting of Sicilian olives",
        "t_7bbf81da": "Cold pressed immediately after harvesting",
        "t_9de4f0d8": "Strict quality control",
        "t_c4a0d22f": "<i class=\"fas fa-leaf\"></i> <span>Our Sicilian Process</span>",
        "t_5e7ed747": "From the Plant<br/> <span class=\"highlight\">to the Bottle</span>",
        "t_0baa2c14": "Every phase of our production process in the lands of San Biagio Platani is taken care of down to the smallest detail to guarantee the highest quality of our Sicilian extra virgin olive oil.",
        "t_ae011e45": "PRUNING",
        "t_8f61d4c3": "Careful care of Sicilian olive trees to ensure optimal growth and superior quality production in our Agrigento lands.",
        "t_405e0e8d": "COLLECTION",
        "t_43839654": "Manual harvesting of the olives at the perfect ripening time to preserve all the polyphenols.",
        "t_43b0c658": "MILLING",
        "t_ed9e2252": "Cold pressing within 24 hours of harvesting to keep the organoleptic properties of our organic oil intact.",
        "t_ca4c6b06": "DECANTATION",
        "t_f892d7a8": "Natural separation of the oil from the water through a natural and controlled decantation process according to the Sicilian tradition.",
        "t_e9e3133a": "BOTTLING",
        "t_ae091356": "Packaging in dark glass bottles to protect the Sicilian oil from light and oxidation.",
        "t_1e89a0ae": "PACKAGING",
        "t_f8c72de9": "Final labeling and packaging with rigorous quality controls before distribution from our San Biagio Platani factory.",
        "t_a0488acc": "<a class=\"btn btn-gradient-yellow\" href=\"oliodivaleria.it/qualita.html\"> <span>SCOPRI LA QUALITÀ</span> <i class=\"fas fa-crown\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;\"></i> </a> <a class=\"btn btn-white-outline\" href=\"#contact\"> Per Visite </a>",
        "t_faaf4ec4": "Our operational and administrative offices are located in the heart of Sicily, in San Biagio Platani in the province of Agrigento.",
        "t_4bc26125": "Oil mill and production",
        "t_0589a66d": "Administrative headquarters",
        "t_a145f61a": "Contrada Serre, 19",
        "t_6fe69f6a": "Offices and administration",
        "t_937feb5e": "Company Details",
        "t_6d49371b": "<strong>VAT number:</strong> 02957530849",
        "t_188c8c40": "<strong>Code. Tax:</strong> LCTVLR81D62Z112B",
        "t_be42304f": "<strong>Region:</strong> Sicily",
        "t_62da8bb3": "<strong>Province:</strong> Agrigento (AG)",
        "t_aea9a2d9": "Contact us",
        "t_4c21be06": "We are here to answer your questions and help you choose our Sicilian oil perfect for your culinary needs. Contact us at our offices in San Biagio Platani.",
        "t_d2cec236": "Our Gastronomic Laboratory",
